  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  adult males and females aged &gt; 18 years

          -  symptomatic bradicardia

          -  informed consent signed.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  pregnancy

          -  hemodynamic instability (pulmonary congestion / systolic arterial pressure lower than
             90 mmHg)

          -  body mass index greater than 40 kg/ m2

          -  use of oral anticoagulation

          -  acute coronary syndromes

          -  left ventricle ejection fraction &lt; 45%

          -  presence of any kind of cardiac stimulation device
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
